snippet.title: KUBO 3 NES Game (Physical Release) Trailer
snippet.description:
KUBO 3, my recent NES homebrew game, is available on an NES cartridge, a special limited edition complete in box! (only 50 copies)

Contact me directly to order your copy.
(update 04/08/2020: there are no more copies, all copies have been sold! However, possibility to order the cartridge only version, without box or manual)

For more infos on the game or to download the free rom: 
https://dale-coop.itch.io/kubo-3-nes-game-by-sj-games

#NES #homebrew #neshomebrew #retrogaming
